<-- Root Directory -->

1. npm init -y
2. npm i express axios mongoose cookie-parser dotenv jsonwebtoken
3. package.json type, dev and main setting
4. npm i nodemon -D then package.json dev setting

<-- Frontend Directory -->

1. npm create vite@latest .
2. npm i axios lucide-react react-player react-hot-toast react-router-dom zustand
3. ESLint extension
4. App.css delete and all it's import in App.tsx
5. Delete assests and index.css' content
6. Initialize tailwindcss (config file change, index.css has all imports, app.tsx for demo run in return)
7. tailwindcss extension
8. main.tsx has BrowserRouter import and structure
9. App.tsx import route, routes and return the folder structure
10. add fonts using download as assests and tailwind.config.js it
11. add caraousel using npm i react slick
